title: Humburg's Eck
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, International, Beer/Wine, German, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Many vegetarian dishes on the menu, which, according to the cook, can be made upon request with soy cream, oat milk, and coconut milk. Sample veg dishes include the creamed mushroom and the vegetable curry with smoked tofu. Book ahead if you have a large group, and the cook will stock more vegan ingredients.
